            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Duliceno <note>sic</note> <lb n="3"/>ubi fer<expan><ex>r</ex><abbr>um</abbr></expan> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">nascit</supplied>ur </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <abbr>T</abbr> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <abbr>F</abbr><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei nicht aneinanderpassende Fragmente einer Tabula ansata; Schreibtechnik: gepunzt. Z. 5 (T) und Z. 6 (F) stehen auf der linken bzw. rechten ansa. Z. 6: statt F auch E möglich.</p>
            </div>
